text:
"Cute? Sexy?
Which type of Fuyu-chan do you like!?"

──...and with that
we're raking in the responses!

Well then, let's get right into reading them〜
Here, let's start with these!

Radio Name: Usane-san
"Fuyu-chan is cute. Cute is Fuyu-chan!"

Radio Name: LoveF-san
"Your dancing with Straylight is so seductive, I want to kneel down."

Usane-san, LoveF-san, thank you very much!
This is a little embarrasing, huh...

Ahaha, that's the whole point you know〜. Today we'll be talking 
non-stop about the loveable Fuyu-chan's charm. Prepare yourself!

Wah! Fufu...! It's embassing, but I'm also so happy!
I'll steel myself and do my best♡
